# ⭐ **Project‑Wide .gitignore (Python + Pipenv + RAG)**

```gitignore
# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Virtual environments
venv/
.venv/
python-envs/

# Pipenv artifacts
*.lock.bak

# Downloads / scraped files
downloads/
data/raw/
data/processed/

# Vectorstore files
*.bin
*.faiss
*.index

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Logs
*.log

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# VS Code
.vscode/

